They pointed the telescope
at a very narrow piece of sky

00:20:21.730 --> 00:20:25.150
and collect light for
a very long time, OK?

00:20:25.150 --> 00:20:27.802
So they can see stuff
that is really far away.

00:20:27.802 --> 00:20:30.260
So when you look at a picture
like that, you say, oh, yeah.

00:20:30.260 --> 00:20:30.760
Color.

00:20:30.760 --> 00:20:32.030
There are some galaxies here.

